data.description: Discover the charm of this beautiful home in the Arran Hills neighborhood. Featuring 4 bedrooms and 2.1 bathrooms, this residence combines classic comfort with modern living. Central to its charm is a recently upgraded kitchen, now boasting sleek granite countertops and a versatile island. The finished basement offers additional space, ideal for a variety of uses. Parking is a breeze with a spacious, 2-car garage. Experience a blend of suburban tranquility and city convenience in this Fayetteville gem, ready to be called your home. The sale of this distinguished property includes the adjacent parcel, 1306 Bingham Drive, as a comprehensive package. This additional land lot, already cleared and zoned for residential use, offers immense potential for expansion, customization, or development.
